@startuml pattern_abstract_factory
title Abstract Factory Pattern - User Registration Families

interface UserFactory {
  +create(...): User
  +isValidIdentity(String): boolean
  +requiresApproval(): boolean
}

class StudentFactory
class FacultyFactory
class ResearcherFactory
class GuestFactory
class UserFactoryProvider
class RegisterFrame
class User

UserFactory <|.. StudentFactory
UserFactory <|.. FacultyFactory
UserFactory <|.. ResearcherFactory
UserFactory <|.. GuestFactory

RegisterFrame --> UserFactoryProvider : getFactory(UserType)
UserFactoryProvider --> UserFactory
UserFactory --> User : create()

note right of RegisterFrame
Req1: user registration families
Req3: user type drives pricing
end note

@enduml
